		        <p>+ Ph&#7843;n &#273;&#7897;ng, ch&#7889;ng ph&aacute;, b&agrave;i x&iacute;ch t&ocirc;n gi&aacute;o, khi&ecirc;u d&acirc;m, b&#7841;o l&#7921;c, &#273;i ng&#432;&#7907;c l&#7841;i thu&#7847;n phong m&#7929; t&#7909;c, truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng v&agrave; v&#259;n h&oacute;a Vi&#7879;t Nam;</p>
		        <p>+ &#272;&#259;ng th&ocirc;ng tin r&aacute;c, ph&aacute; r&#7889;i hay l&agrave;m m&#7845;t uy t&iacute;n c&#7911;a c&aacute;c d&#7883;ch v&#7909; do Shopee cung c&#7845;p;</p>
		        <p>+ X&uacute;c ph&#7841;m, kh&iacute;ch b&aacute;c &#273;&#7871;n ng&#432;&#7901;i kh&aacute;c d&#432;&#7899;i b&#7845;t k&#7923; h&igrave;nh th&#7913;c n&agrave;o;</p>
		        <p>+ Tuy&ecirc;n truy&#7873;n v&#7873; nh&#7919;ng th&ocirc;ng tin m&agrave; ph&aacute;p lu&#7853;t nghi&ecirc;m c&#7845;m nh&#432;: s&#7917; d&#7909;ng heroin, thu&#7889;c l&#7855;c, gi&#7871;t ng&#432;&#7901;i, c&#432;&#7899;p c&#7911;a,vv (VD: s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m in h&igrave;nh l&aacute; c&#7847;n sa, shisha);</p>
