		          <li>Khi qu&agrave; t&#7863;ng k&egrave;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#259;ng c&ocirc;ng khai tr&ecirc;n th&ocirc;ng tin s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m ch&iacute;nh, quy &#273;&#7883;nh v&#7873; h&#7841;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &aacute;p d&#7909;ng t&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m ch&iacute;nh.</li>
		          <li>Khi qu&agrave; t&#7863;ng k&egrave;m kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#259;ng c&ocirc;ng khai tr&ecirc;n th&ocirc;ng tin s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m ch&iacute;nh, Shopee s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng can thi&#7879;p x&#7917; l&yacute; khi&#7871;u n&#7841;i v&#7873; h&#7841;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&#7911;a qu&agrave; t&#7863;ng k&egrave;m. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n h&agrave;nh vi c&#7889; &yacute; t&#7863;ng k&egrave;m s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m h&#7871;t h&#7841;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; mang &#273;&#7871;n tr&#7843;i nghi&#7879;m kh&ocirc;ng t&#7889;t cho Ng&#432;&#7901;i Mua v&agrave; l&agrave;m gi&#7843;m uy t&iacute;n c&#7911;a Ng&#432;&#7901;i B&aacute;n th&ocirc;ng qua vi&#7879;c &#273;&aacute;nh gi&aacute; k&eacute;m t&#7915; Ng&#432;&#7901;i Mua tr&ecirc;n &#273;&#417;n h&agrave;ng.</li>
	            </ul>
		        <p>4/ X&#7917; l&yacute; vi ph&#7841;m&nbsp;</p>
      <p>Ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng vi ph&#7841;m m&#7897;t trong c&aacute;c quy &#273;&#7883;nh tr&ecirc;n v&#7873; h&#7841;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&#7911;a s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m, t&ugrave;y theo m&#7913;c &#273;&#7897; vi ph&#7841;m, Shopee s&#7869; ti&#7871;n h&agrave;nh m&#7897;t s&#7889; bi&#7879;n ph&aacute;p x&#7917; l&yacute; ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p nh&#432; x&oacute;a s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m, kh&oacute;a t&agrave;i kho&#7843;n, y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u ng&#432;&#7901;i b&aacute;n &#273;&#7873;n b&ugrave; thi&#7879;t h&#7841;i cho ng&#432;&#7901;i mua,v.v...</p>
		        <p><strong>Khuy&#7871;n c&aacute;o:</strong><em>Ng&#432;&#7901;i b&aacute;n vui l&ograve;ng t&ocirc;n tr&#7885;ng v&agrave; tu&acirc;n th&#7911; quy &#273;&#7883;nh &#273;&#259;ng b&aacute;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&#7911;a Shopee. M&#7885;i s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m kh&ocirc;ng tu&acirc;n th&#7911; theo c&aacute;c quy &#273;&#7883;nh, h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n tr&ecirc;n s&#7869; b&#7883; kh&oacute;a/x&oacute;a m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o tr&#432;&#7899;c. Ng&#432;&#7901;i b&aacute;n s&#7869; ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n tr&#432;&#7899;c Ph&aacute;p lu&#7853;t n&#7871;u c&#7889; t&igrave;nh &#273;&#259;ng t&#7843;i c&aacute;c n&#7897;i dung m&agrave; Ph&aacute;p lu&#7853;t Vi&#7879;t Nam kh&ocirc;ng cho ph&eacute;p./.</em></p>
